    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Miuratale: Dive into Adventure</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a boundless underwater world, three mermaid kingdoms, the Miura, Seeka, and Atla, struggle for unity amidst a rising tide of darkness. A mysterious power returns, threatening to engulf the seas. Only a Trident Warrior can stand against the tide, and this time fate has called upon an unlikely hero to wield its immense power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Keena as she journeys across the sunken world of Aegea and discover ancient treasures, powerful relics, friends, allies, and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the Unknown:</strong> From vibrant reefs to haunting abysses, navigate a world teeming with secrets, trials, and treasures as Keena dives deeper into danger!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Combat:</strong> Master the power of the Spirit Trident with fast , fluid action. Unlock elemental abilities, powerful special abilities, and take on the chaotic enemies of Corruption!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expressive Customization:</strong> Collecting resources all over the seabed and craft armor in your workshop, brew potions in your laboratory, and cook stat boosting meals in your cookery!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A New Mermaid World:</strong> Unravel a total new universe inspired by Greek mythology and mermaid culture. Meet the various mermaid cultures of the sea and learn their history in a 50,000+ word script!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Underwater Puzzles:</strong> Take on challenges from the gods, navigate ancient technology, and solve the Siren Seal's as you discover the mechanism's of an primordial enemy.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will Keena rise above the waves of darkness, or will the ocean’s final light fade forever? Find out in <i>Miuratale</i>.</p>",
